snippet.title: PBA® Bowling Challenge - Official Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Here is the official trailer for PBA Bowling Challenge, the best free bowling game on mobile!

Get it on iPhone/iPad: https://itunes.apple.com/app/id657459418
Also available on Google Play: http://bit.ly/W6NdIw
And Kindle Fire: http://amzn.to/Y3lGd0

Rise through the ranks of the PBA as you compete in the top regional and national championships, competing against 21 of the biggest names in bowling in over a dozen different venues. Upgrade your equipment and hone your skills in the most complete bowling experience on mobile. This is PBA Bowling Challenge!

Like us: http://www.facebook.com/ConcreteSoftware
Follow us: http://www.twitter.com/ConcreteGames
